text:
On Thursday pay pensions in Ullum
04 Nov 2019 by Cuyo Daily Writing
From the Municipality of Ullum they informed that the Argentine Post Office will pay pensions and pensions to the beneficiaries of the department. Payment of this benefit will be made next Thursday from 9.30 to 12, in the municipal building. The beneficiaries must bring the ID to access the payment.
